---
title: 'Kontakt | Šah klub Končar'
layout: 'base.njk'
---

  
  <head>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/kontakt.css" />
    <meta name="description" content="Kontaktirajte nas! Postavite nam pitanja i pridružite nam se. Otvoreni smo za svaku suranju.">
    <meta name="keywords"content="Šah, Zagreb, igrati šah, trenirati šah, šah klub, šahovski klub, šahovski klub Zagreb, škola šaha">
  </head>

    <main aria-labelledby="contact-title" id="main-content">
      <div class="section">
        <div class="max-width-wrapper">
          <div class="title-container">
            <h1 id="contact-title" class="fs-700 ff-sans">Kontakt</h1>
            <hr />
          </div>
          <div class="contact-container">
            <div class="form-container">
              <div class="form-text">
                <h2 class="fs-600">Kontaktirajte nas!</h2>
                <p>Molimo Vas da nas kontaktirate preko sljedećeg obrasca.</p>
              </div>
              <form name="contact" method="POST" data-netlify="true">
                <p>
                  <label for="name">Ime i prezime*</label>
                  <input
                    type="text"
                    name="name"
                    id="name"
                    required
                    placeholder="Ana Horvat"
                  />
                </p>
                <p>
                  <label for="email">E-mail*</label>
                  <input
                    type="email"
                    name="email"
                    id="email"
                    required
                    placeholder="ana.horvat@gmail.com"
                  />
                </p>
                <p>
                  <label for="phone">Mobitel</label>
                  <input
                    type="phone"
                    name="phone"
                    id="phone"
                    placeholder="091 5050 505"
                  />
                </p>

                <p>
                  <label for="message">Poruka*</label>
                  <textarea
                    name="message"
                    id="message"
                    cols="30"
                    rows="10"
                    required
                    placeholder="Radujemo se Vašoj poruci :)"
                  ></textarea>
                </p>

                <div class="recaptcha">
                  <div data-netlify-recaptcha="true"></div>
                </div>

                <p>
                  <button type="submit">Pošalji</button>
                </p>
              </form>
              <p class="max-width-70ch">
                Alternativno, možete nas kontaktirati putem emaila
                <a href="mailto:sah.klub@koncar.hr">sah.klub@koncar.hr</a>,
                društvenih mreža i na broj mobitela 091 6250 007 (Bruno Pavčević
                - Dopredsjednik).
              </p>
            </div>
            <div class="map-container">
              <h2 class="fs-600 map-title">Gdje se nalazimo?</h2>
              <div class="map-responsive">
                <iframe
                  src="https://www.google.com/maps/embed?pb=!1m14!1m8!1m3!1d11125.920703466236!2d15.9341084!3d45.801641!3m2!1i1024!2i768!4f13.1!3m3!1m2!1s0x0%3A0x39840fd5010adeb0!2zxaBhaCBrbHViIEtvbsSNYXI!5e0!3m2!1sen!2shr!4v1597003877765!5m2!1sen!2shr"
                  width="600"
                  height="450"
                  frameborder="0"
                  style="border: 0"
                  allowfullscreen=""
                  aria-hidden="false"
                  tabindex="0"
                ></iframe>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </main>
